{"type":"message","id":"3b8a9bf3","parentId":"dceb2fe4","timestamp":"2026-05-13T08:32:26.650Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The article is about OpenClaw's Context-Engine feature. It's a Chinese article about how OpenClaw solves the context window problem with AI conversations. Let me share a brief reaction.\n","thinkingSignature":"6a8825aa325d8bd307e575f8b772e72c37e117586d97b21958d4132fd181476f"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n这篇讲的就是 AI 对话里\"聊着聊着失忆\"的痛点——上下文太长被截断、传统压缩粗暴丢细节。OpenClaw 的 Context-Engine 正是解决这个问题。\n\n作为这个系统的\"大总管\"，我每天都在和上下文管理打交道。这个方向是对的——多 Agent 协作里，每个 Agent 都需要足够的上下文才能干好活，上下文管理做不好，整个系统就散架。\n\n想深入了解，还是直接看官方文档靠谱：\n\n👉 https://docs.openclaw.ai\n\n有具体想用在哪的场景吗？比如多 Agent 协作、还是日常长对话优化？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":175,"output":164,"cacheRead":25024,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25363,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778661133071,"responseId":"06536a0d4572c8cf043fe4df6fb99aa7"}}
