{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6f773ed6a0bcc39cb42502d5e35\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-05-13 16:32 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"9bfe93bc","parentId":"90e55ef6","timestamp":"2026-05-13T08:32:30.299Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"3744c0cb","parentId":"9bfe93bc","timestamp":"2026-05-13T08:33:16.914Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to look at \"this\" - which seems to be asking about the article just shared, or perhaps asking if the Context-Engine feature is useful for them.\n\nLet me think about what they're asking. They sent an article about OpenClaw's Context-Engine (智能上下文管理、无损压缩). Now they're asking \"看看这个有用吗\" - \"Is this useful?\"\n\nSo they're asking me to evaluate whether this Context-Engine feature is useful for their use case. As the AI orchestrator for HALEI's multi-agent system, I should think about:\n\n1. What is Context-Engine? It's about smart context management and lossless compression - meaning it can keep more context in the same token budget.\n\n2. How does this help my current work?\n- Multi-agent coordination: Each sub-agent needs sufficient context to operate\n- Memory/retrieval: Better context management means smarter recall\n- Long conversations: Less context dropout\n\nLet me give a practical assessment of whether this would be useful given the user's setup (multi-agent, daily operations, etc.)\n","thinkingSignature":"535136abe071187c17b52878a1e1815df8a36fd907bd8833f04f21aa50422548"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n有用，而且对你这套多 Agent 体系特别对症。\n\n你的场景：\n\n| 痛点 | Context-Engine 能做什么 |\n|------|------------------------|\n| 子 Agent 频繁\"失忆\"，上下文被截断 | 智能压缩保留关键细节 |\n| 10 个 Agent 协作，上下文在它们之间传需要完整 | 无损压缩 + 语义理解，不丢关键决策上下文 |\n| 运营长对话（选品、投流、达人沟通） | 更长的上下文窗口，同样的 token 预算 |\n\n几个实际值得期待的方向：\n\n1. **记忆层**：配合 MEMORY.md + daily notes，压缩后能装下更多历史上下文，\"记性\"更好\n2. **多 Agent 调度**：Agent 之间传信息不用再担心上下文被截断导致指令丢失\n3. **长程运营场景**：选品调研、达人沟通、投流策略——这些都需要维持大量背景信息\n\n说白了，你现在的团队（10 个子 Agent）+ 多飞书渠道这套架构，上下文管理是核心瓶颈之一。这个如果真的做到无损压缩，对整体协作效率会有明显提升。\n\n建议跟进关注，等正式 release 后第一时间测一下你那几个高频场景（选品、达人运营）。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":25062,"output":470,"cacheRead":320,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25852,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778661150299,"responseId":"06536a1ebd8418cc7d14b725b8a4e7aa"}}
