{"type":"message","id":"c85cf733","parentId":"43c2aeb2","timestamp":"2026-05-13T09:24:54.645Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_vqnn1ifx0fvh_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"│ @martian-    │ lossless │ openclaw │ enabled  │ ~/.openclaw/npm/node_modules/@martian-engineering/       │ 0.9.4     │\n│ engineering/ │ -claw    │          │          │ lossless-claw/dist/index.js                              │           │\n│ lossless-    │          │          │          │                                                          │           │\n│ claw         │          │          │          │                                                          │           │\n│ @openclaw/   │ feishu   │ openclaw │ enabled  │ ~/.openclaw/npm/node_modules/@openclaw/feishu/dist/      │ 2026.5.4  │"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":9643,"aggregated":"│ @martian-    │ lossless │ openclaw │ enabled  │ ~/.openclaw/npm/node_modules/@martian-engineering/       │ 0.9.4     │\n│ engineering/ │ -claw    │          │          │ lossless-claw/dist/index.js                              │           │\n│ lossless-    │          │          │          │                                                          │           │\n│ claw         │          │          │          │                                                          │           │\n│ @openclaw/   │ feishu   │ openclaw │ enabled  │ ~/.openclaw/npm/node_modules/@openclaw/feishu/dist/      │ 2026.5.4  │","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778664294644}}
{"type":"message","id":"52d73ae3","parentId":"c85cf733","timestamp":"2026-05-13T09:24:54.648Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6f7078f40094c357a247198a00a\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-05-13 17:24 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b6f7078f40094c357a247198a00a]\nou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb: 另外一个问题就是，你不是说他可以把这些Agent的上下文都统一进行记录吗？\n\n那我们现在遇到一个问题就是，整个跨境电商团队大概7~8个Agent，那个比方他们怎么去沟通呢？或者是，比如说运营总监的这个Agent怎么和其他所有的Agent来进行通信、下发指令呢？"}],"timestamp":1778664294120}}
{"type":"message","id":"3a450636","parentId":"52d73ae3","timestamp":"2026-05-13T09:27:22.369Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a great question. The user is asking about inter-Agent communication. With 7-8 agents in their cross-border e-commerce team, how do they communicate with each other? How does the director agent send instructions to other agents?\n\nLet me think about this from the OpenClaw multi-agent architecture perspective and the user's specific setup.\n\nIn the current architecture:\n- Each Agent has its own workspace, identity, and session\n- There's a binding system that routes messages from specific Feishu accounts to specific agents\n- The main agent (KIIT) can use sessions_send to send messages to other agents\n\nBut the user's question is about: how do agents communicate with each other automatically? Specifically:\n1. How does the director agent communicate with other agents?\n2. How do agents coordinate with each other?\n\nLooking at the current setup, the communication pattern seems to be:\n- Feishu user → KIIT (main) → sub-agents via sessions_send\n- But agent-to-agent communication isn't clearly structured\n\nThe user wants:\n- Director Agent → other agents: issuing instructions, coordination\n- Possibly: sub-agents reporting back to director\n\nThis is a multi-agent orchestration question. Let me think about practical approaches:\n\n1. **Shared memory/workspace files**: Director writes to shared files, other agents read\n2. **sessions_send**: KIIT or Director uses sessions_send to coordinate\n3. **Feishu group chat**: Multiple agents in same group can communicate\n4. **Task queue pattern**: Agents pick up tasks from a queue\n\nCurrent bindings show each agent has its own Feishu account (kiit, tts, agent-orchestrator, content, traffic, ops, director, finance, review, koc). They each have their own \"inbox\" via Feishu.\n\nBut the key question is: how does Director (运营总监) automatically send instructions to content, traffic, ops, koc, etc.?\n\n\nThe director agent could leverage sessions_send to directly communicate with sub-agents through OpenClaw's inter-agent messaging, or write coordination data to shared workspace files that other agents monitor. The current setup with kiit, tts, and other agents is already distributed by design, which provides a foundation for this kind of coordination. Each sub-agent operates as an independent session, so the orchestrator can route messages to specific agents as needed. For the user's cross-border e-commerce setup with a Director at the top, the workflow would be: HALEI assigns objectives to the Director via Feishu, the Director then delegates to specialized agents (TTS, Content, KOC, Traffic), and those agents execute and report results back through the same channel. This is essentially what the agent-orchestrator agent handles—coordination rather than direct execution. I should outline the actual communication patterns and offer to configure the Feishu group structure to support this hierarchy.\n","thinkingSignature":"0c3f300d64ad0703b50291098bba4db6b5e729cd3acf6fabb8e2673b948566f3"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n这是个核心编排问题。让我先说清楚现在的通信架构，然后看怎么让 Director Agent 能真正\"下发指令\"。\n\n## 当前架构\n\n目前各 Agent 是**各自独立的会话**，通信靠：\n1. **sessions_send** — 主 Agent（KIIT）手动发消息给子 Agent\n2. **Feishu 账号体系** — 每个 Agent 有独立飞书账号，相当于独立\"收件箱\"\n\n```json\nkiit        → 主控（你直接对话）\ntts         → 选品大师\ncontent     → 内容专家\ntraffic     → 投流专家\nops         → 运营助手\ndirector    → 运营总监\nfinance     → 财务助手\nreview      → 评论专家\nkoc         → 达人运营\n```\n\n## 问题：Director Agent 如何下发指令？\n\n说实话，**目前_DIRECTOR_这个 Agent 还没有自动下发指令的能力**。它只能：\n- 接收人类指令（通过飞书）\n- 被动响应\n\n要让 Director 真正做\"总指挥\"，需要**主动协调机制**。有几种方案：\n\n---\n\n### 方案 A：任务队列 + 定期轮询（推荐）\n\nDirector Agent 定时检查任务队列，向各 Agent 下发指令：\n\n```\nDirector Agent（定时）\n  ↓ 轮询任务队列\n  ↓ 发现\"内容团队需要本周选题计划\"\n  ↓ sessions_send → content Agent\n  ↓ sessions_send → koc Agent\n  \ncontent/koc 执行 → 结果写回共享workspace\nDirector 下一轮检查结果，继续调度\n```\n\n**实现方式**：给 Director 开一个 cron job，每 30 分钟运行一次，检查共享文件中是否有待下发指令。\n\n---\n\n### 方案 B：群聊协调\n\n所有 Agent 加入同一个飞书群，Director 在群里发指令，其他 Agent 监听并响应。\n\n```\n飞书群：TK 跨境电商团队\n  └── director（运营总监）\n  └── content（内容专家）\n  └── traffic（投流专家）\n  └── ops（运营助手）\n  └── ...\n\ndirector 发：\"@内容专家 本周重点做家居品类视频脚本\"\ncontent 接收 → 执行\n```\n\n**实现方式**：建飞书群，把各 Agent 的飞书账号都拉进去。\n\n---\n\n### 方案 C：父子 Agent 链式调用\n\nKIIT 收到任务 → 分配给 Director → Director 再分配给子 Agent。\n\n```\n你 → KIIT（编排）\n     ↓\n     Director（父 Agent，协调）\n     ↓ sessions_send\n     ├── TTS（选品）\n     ├── Content（内容）\n     ├── Traffic（投流）\n     └── KOC（达人）\n```\n\n这是**编排模式**的实现，需要打开 `context:\"fork\"` 让 Director 能获取完整上下文。\n\n---\n\n## 我的建议\n\n**方案 A + 方案 C 结合**，最实际：\n\n1. 你通过 KIIT 下发本周目标给 Director\n2. Director 每隔一段时间自动轮询，有任务就通过 sessions_send 下发给各子 Agent\n3. 各子 Agent 完成后写回共享文件，Director 汇总结果\n\n要我帮你搭建这套协调机制吗？具体要：\n- 配置 Director 的定时调度\n- 搭建共享任务文件格式\n- 定义各 Agent 之间的通信协议\n\n先搞清楚你们的业务流优先级：日常是**谁向谁发指令**最频繁？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":41458,"output":1271,"cacheRead":25408,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68137,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778664294649,"responseId":"06537667bd392b6d6de90278dee99acf"}}
{"type":"message","id":"7f3aeb4b","parentId":"3a450636","timestamp":"2026-05-13T09:27:22.372Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6f7078373c54c2620f0328cc5a0\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-05-13 17:25 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b6f7078373c54c2620f0328cc5a0]\nou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb: 是走飞书互通，还是走OpenClaw底层的互通？"}],"timestamp":1778664305628}}
{"type":"message","id":"7b29d00f","parentId":"7f3aeb4b","timestamp":"2026-05-13T09:28:31.820Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking whether the communication between agents goes through Feishu or through OpenClaw's internal messaging system (sessions_send).\n\nLet me explain the two options clearly:\n\n1. **Feishu (飞书)**: Agents communicate via their Feishu bot accounts - messages go through the Feishu platform, each agent has its own inbox\n2. **OpenClaw internal (sessions_send)**: Agents communicate via OpenClaw's internal session messaging - no external dependency, faster, but no external visibility\n\nLet me give a clear comparison.\n","thinkingSignature":"615e16b3b93d0541b556555457f226548a9e193d99556fcdd83c51bc120e597f"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n好问题。两条路：\n\n## 方案对比\n\n| | 飞书互通 | OpenClaw 内部互通 |\n|---|---|---|\n| **通道** | 各 Agent 飞书账号 → 飞书消息 | `sessions_send` → 内部 API |\n| **延迟** | 慢（依赖飞书服务器） | 快（本地进程） |\n| **可追溯** | 飞书里能看到对话记录 | 日志里看，外部不可见 |\n| **容错** | 飞书挂了就断 | Gateway 活着就能通 |\n| **人工干预** | 方便，人类随时进群看 | 人类看不到内部消息 |\n\n## 推荐：内部为主 + 飞书做备\n\n```\nDirector Agent\n  ├── sessions_send → 各子Agent（日常，毫秒级）\n  └── 重要指令同时发飞书（可审计、可干预）\n```\n\n**对于你们的场景**：\n- 运营指令、任务分配 → 用 `sessions_send`（内部，快）\n- 人类需要知道/介入 → 同时发飞书\n- 跨天的大任务 → 结果写共享文件，Human 下一步再看\n\n## 实际配置\n\n要开启这套，我需要给 Director Agent 加一个**定期协调循环**：\n\n1. 共享任务池文件（JSON）\n2. Director 每 N 分钟检查任务池\n3. 有任务 → sessions_send 下发 + 飞书抄送\n4. 子 Agent 执行 → 写回结果\n5. Director 汇总 → 给你汇报\n\n**现在最大的问题是**：你们日常的指令流是什么样的？\n\n举例：\n> 每天早上运营总监要告诉选品团队\"本周主推什么品类\" → 内容团队\"本周出几篇内容\" → 投流团队\"预算怎么分配\"\n\n这个链条是谁触发的？你（人）→ KIIT → Director？还是 Director 自己定时触发？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1021,"output":502,"cacheRead":66816,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68339,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778664442373,"responseId":"065376fa68712181006ed99c72a4be45"}}
{"type":"message","id":"1acf2320","parentId":"7b29d00f","timestamp":"2026-05-13T09:32:31.083Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[message_id: om_x100b6f701c55d88cc2134915a978804]\nou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb: 两个问题：\n1. 你说的这个“内部为主，飞书作备”我同意。反正也是通过飞书发送指令，它同样还可以实现这个功能，实际上是两端都可以。\n 主要就是通过飞书的消息，也是通过内部的消息机制来进行协作互通。\n2. 你刚才装的那个企业版的东西有没有作用呢？你不能说我装，你就找一个差不多就装上了"}],"timestamp":1778664751060}}
{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6f701c55d88cc2134915a978804\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-05-13 17:32 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"ca6b56ef","parentId":"1acf2320","timestamp":"2026-05-13T09:32:31.106Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"cd8d25a1","parentId":"ca6b56ef","timestamp":"2026-05-13T09:33:37.529Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking two things:\n\n1. **Communication channel**: Should it go through Feishu interoperability or OpenClaw's internal messaging mechanism? The user agrees with \"internal first, Feishu as backup\" approach - meaning both channels work, but internal is primary.\n\n2. **Lossless-Claw effectiveness**: The user is questioning whether the lossless-claw I installed actually works or if I just grabbed something random. They're right to call this out - I need to verify that it's actually functioning and not just \"a random plugin that looks similar.\"\n\nLet me address both:\n\n### 1. Communication Channel\nThe user wants **both**:\n- OpenClaw internal messaging (`sessions_send`) as primary\n- Feishu as backup (Director can also receive/send via Feishu if needed)\n\nThat's exactly the hybrid approach I was describing. Both are valid channels. The key is defining the protocol so that instructions delivered via either channel are interpreted the same way.\n\n### 2. Lossless-Claw - Is it actually working?\nI installed it and saw it in the plugin list as \"enabled\", but the user is right to question whether it's actually doing anything. I should:\n\n1. Verify the plugin is actually loaded and functioning\n2. Check if the context engine is actually active\n3. Run a quick test to see if lossless-claw is being used\n\nLet me do some verification.\n","thinkingSignature":"d219115fd311d7e530f4497cdc73b34532f99e8d55775c43b77e4f22385ddf48"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n两个问题都重要，一个个来。\n\n## 1. 通信：飞书 + OpenClaw 底层双通道\n\n你的思路对——**两条路都通，互为备份**：\n\n```\n你 → KIIT（主对话）\n     ↓ sessions_send（内部优先）\n     ├── Director（运营总监）\n     │      ↓ sessions_send\n     │      ├── TTS / Content / Traffic / KOC / ...\n     │\n     └── Director 也可以通过飞书账号发消息给各 Agent\n        （飞书相当于\"人工介入\"通道）\n```\n\n**实际场景**：日常协作走 `sessions_send`（OpenClaw 内部），响应快、不依赖外部网络。如果某条消息失败，再通过飞书发指令兜底。\n\n---\n\n## 2. Lossless-Claw 有没有真正在干活？\n\n你说得对，不能装完就完事了。让我验证一下它到底有没有生效：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_vdhrhwzgi90x_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw plugins list 2>&1 | grep -A3 \"lossless\"","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":50660,"output":521,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51181,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778664751211,"responseId":"0653782f25c81c022ea6467335cb953f"}}
{"type":"message","id":"a395106e","parentId":"cd8d25a1","timestamp":"2026-05-13T09:33:41.093Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_vdhrhwzgi90x_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"│ @martian-    │ lossless │ openclaw │ enabled  │ ~/.openclaw/npm/node_modules/@martian-engineering/       │ 0.9.4     │\n│ engineering/ │ -claw    │          │          │ lossless-claw/dist/index.js                              │           │\n│ lossless-    │          │          │          │                                                          │           │\n│ claw         │          │          │          │                                                          │           │\n│ @openclaw/   │ feishu   │ openclaw │ enabled  │ ~/.openclaw/npm/node_modules/@openclaw/feishu/dist/      │ 2026.5.4  │\n│ feishu       │          │          │          │ index.js                                                 │           │"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":3312,"aggregated":"│ @martian-    │ lossless │ openclaw │ enabled  │ ~/.openclaw/npm/node_modules/@martian-engineering/       │ 0.9.4     │\n│ engineering/ │ -claw    │          │          │ lossless-claw/dist/index.js                              │           │\n│ lossless-    │          │          │          │                                                          │           │\n│ claw         │          │          │          │                                                          │           │\n│ @openclaw/   │ feishu   │ openclaw │ enabled  │ ~/.openclaw/npm/node_modules/@openclaw/feishu/dist/      │ 2026.5.4  │\n│ feishu       │          │          │          │ index.js                                                 │           │","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778664821092}}
{"type":"message","id":"fedff159","parentId":"a395106e","timestamp":"2026-05-13T09:33:51.250Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me verify what lossless-claw actually does by checking the SKILL.md of its plugin-skills version that was installed.\n","thinkingSignature":"3ca9daca1499b20858a1a6284614e96c5e794eee5d0081aa63a2ce38ea30fc3b"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_2ovxiedwqzuh_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/ | grep -i loss; ls ~/.openclaw/plugin-skills/ 2>/dev/null | grep -i loss; ls ~/.openclaw/extensions/ 2>/dev/null | grep -i loss","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":252,"output":111,"cacheRead":50624,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50987,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778664821104,"responseId":"0653787513731249df34dde0ae985c19"}}
