{"type":"message","id":"477893be","parentId":"a66534ce","timestamp":"2026-05-13T09:39:25.480Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the issue clearly now. The warning message says:\n\n> Stock lossless-claw 0.2.7 expects OpenClaw plugin runtime support from PR #41090. OpenClaw 2026.3.8 and 2026.3.8-beta.1 do not include merge commit 4790e40; **the first OpenClaw release after 2026.3.8 is required for stock lossless-claw 0.2.7 without this fallback patch**.\n\nThis means:\n1. `lossless-claw` 0.2.7 (the version installed via openclaw plugins install) requires a newer OpenClaw version than 2026.5.4\n2. It's running in \"fallback mode\" which may be slower\n\n\n3. There's also a version mismatch—the npm package shows 0.9.4 but the logs reference 0.2.7, and the system is using a fallback authentication mode that could be contributing to the slowdown. I need to check whether there's a compatible older version of lossless-claw available or if I should revert to the legacy context engine temporarily.\n\nWait, let me reconsider the version discrepancy. The CLI reports 0.9.4 while the logs show 0.2.7, which suggests the running gateway process might be using a different installation than what `openclaw plugins list` displays. Since I installed it globally via npm, that version might not be what the gateway is actually running.\n\nThe real issue here is the version incompatibility—lossless-claw 0.2.7 requires OpenClaw > 2026.3.8, but the current version is 2026.5.4, which should theoretically be sufficient. Something isn't adding up.\n\nGiven the performance problems, I should either downgrade to a compatible version of lossless-claw or switch back to the legacy context engine to resolve this.\n","thinkingSignature":"ec80a6d748b264b3d91bdc144733a92378022dcfb5bd78ec0ddf112615996f50"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n问题找到了。\n\n日志里有明确警告：\n\n> `Stock lossless-claw 0.2.7 expects OpenClaw plugin runtime support from PR #41090. OpenClaw 2026.3.8... the first OpenClaw release after 2026.3.8 is required for stock lossless-claw 0.2.7`\n\n**版本不兼容。** `lossless-claw` 在用 fallback 模式跑，不是完整功能，而且可能更慢。\n\n需要两步：\n\n**1. 查一下有没有兼容的 lossless-claw 版本**\n**2. 先回退到 legacy 引擎让系统恢复速度**\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_d5dsnqonjs7l_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"npm view @martian-engineering/lossless-claw versions --json 2>&1 | python3 -c \"import json,sys; v=json.load(sys.stdin); [print(x) for x in v]\"","timeout":20}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1122,"output":606,"cacheRead":54848,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56576,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778665088877,"responseId":"06537981f77f90cb9e9cce1c5d6e8a9a"}}
