{"type":"message","id":"5b359f72","parentId":"59d06e0e","timestamp":"2026-05-13T09:45:13.914Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is confirming the status and seems to want to move on. They sent a message that just says \"现在的情况：✅ lossless-claw 已装上并启用 ✅ Context Engine 槽位已切换\" without any actual question. This looks like they're summarizing/stating the current state, possibly waiting for me to acknowledge or move on.\n\nLet me acknowledge and confirm, then circle back to the original unanswered question about the Agent communication architecture.","thinkingSignature":"0241367e6a6d2d26e5d453d387389c41d12edf259ead8674c9666fd01d296907"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n确认收到。\n\n慢是**之前就在跑的老问题**，不是这次装插件导致的——日志里 17:19 就出现了 long-running session，那时候还没装 lossless-claw。\n\n---\n\n## 现在可以继续推进的事\n\n回到你之前问的：**Director Agent 怎么和其他 Agent 通信下发指令**。\n\n两条路都能走通：\n\n| 通道 | 用途 |\n|------|------|\n| `sessions_send` | OpenClaw 内部，毫秒级延迟 |\n| 飞书消息 | 人工可读、可追溯、可干预 |\n\n**建议**：先搭内部通信，重要指令同时走飞书。核心协调逻辑用共享任务文件 + cron 驱动。\n\n要现在搭建这套，还是先把 lossless-claw 用熟、确认它稳定了再说？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":4518,"output":252,"cacheRead":61632,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66402,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778665504521,"responseId":"06537b217c4efd4171bb2295797ff37e"}}
{"type":"message","id":"bdba7a9a","parentId":"5b359f72","timestamp":"2026-05-13T09:45:17.806Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[message_id: om_x100b6f70cea6b884c21d6d79332f8fe]\nou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb: 这两个你什么建议啊？\n\n还有就是，现在后台没有其他在跑的了呀，这是为什么呀？突然间并发速度回复就慢了"}],"timestamp":1778665517784}}
{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6f70cea6b884c21d6d79332f8fe\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-05-13 17:44 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"963c708c","parentId":"bdba7a9a","timestamp":"2026-05-13T09:45:17.807Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"3c23d0b8","parentId":"963c708c","timestamp":"2026-05-13T09:45:47.312Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking two things:\n1. What do I recommend about the two checkmarks (lossless-claw installed and enabled)?\n2. Why is it slow when there's nothing else running in the background?\n\nLet me address both:\n\n1. My recommendation on lossless-claw: Keep it. The warnings are non-critical (version compatibility using legacy auth fallback). The actual functionality works. The main slowness is from MiniMax model latency, not the plugin.\n\n2. Why slow with nothing running: This is the key question. The \"active=1, queued=1\" pattern in the logs means there's always at least one active model call. The sessions are \"long-running\" because MiniMax model is slow to respond. It's not that there are other tasks competing - it's that the model call itself is the bottleneck.\n\n\n3. The event loop utilization is only at 5-16%, which confirms the CPU isn't the constraint—the model itself is the bottleneck, taking hundreds of seconds per call. I should focus on what actually matters here rather than continuing to dig into why the plugin isn't the issue.","thinkingSignature":"6dbf69659719352b9f91225c0b321ef834f8a264f0ddcb5c45ee9e4d1997bc1c"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 1. lossless-claw 建议：留着\n\n- 警告是**非阻断性的** — 用 legacy fallback 绕过去了，功能正常\n- 慢是 MiniMax 模型响应慢，不是这个插件\n- 装回 legacy 不会解决你的问题，只是省去一个 warning\n\n---\n\n## 2. 为什么\"没其他任务在跑\"还是慢\n\n看日志里的数字：\n\n```\neventLoopUtilization = 0.052~0.161   ← 也就 5~16%\nactive=1, queued=1                   ← 只有 1 个在跑，1 个在排队\n```\n\n**CPU 其实很闲**。那慢在哪？\n\n模型调用是**同步阻塞**的。一个请求发到 MiniMax，要等模型跑完才返回。这个等待期间：\n\n```\n你的会话 → 发送请求到MiniMax → 等模型算 → 模型返回 → 才响应你\n                                          ↑\n                                    这段时间什么都干不了\n                               可能等了几百秒，CPU 闲着\n```\n\n日志里的 `age=585s` 就是这个意思——这个 session 等了将近 10 分钟模型返回。\n\n---\n\n## 根因确认\n\n**是 MiniMax M2.7 模型本身响应慢**，不是：\n- ❌ 不是 lossless-claw\n- ❌ 不是 CPU 负载\n- ❌ 不是并发太多\n\n你要快，有两条路：\n\n| 方案 | 做什么 | 效果 |\n|------|--------|------|\n| **A** | 切到更快/更稳定的模型 | 治本，但有成本 |\n| **B** | 先关掉 lossless-claw，等官方修复兼容 | 省去一个潜在风险点，但不影响速度 |\n\n**我的建议**：先保持现状（留着 lossless-claw），因为它不是问题根源。等官方出正式兼容版本再升级。\n\n你们现在 MiniMax 用的是免费还是付费通道？响应这么慢可能是达到了并发/限速。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":717,"output":619,"cacheRead":65824,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67160,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778665517830,"responseId":"06537b2e9056dfdb9d0fc0e3740faf38"}}
