{"type":"message","id":"01b4796f","parentId":"5ed11e0c","timestamp":"2026-05-13T09:46:37.259Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_0r4p5flml1wy_1","toolName":"session_status","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.5.4 (325df3e)\n🧠 Model: minimax/MiniMax-M2.7 · 🔑 api-key (minimax:cn)\n🧮 Tokens: 20k in / 209 out\n🗄️ Cache: 50% hit · 20k cached, 0 new\n📚 Context: 20k/204k (10%) · 🧹 Compactions: 0\n📊 Usage: 5h 16% left ⏱2h 13m\n🧵 Session: agent:main:feishu:kiit:direct:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb • updated 16m ago\n⚙️ Execution: direct · Runtime: OpenClaw Pi Default · Think: adaptive · elevated\n🪢 Queue: steer (depth 0)"}],"details":{"ok":true,"sessionKey":"agent:main:feishu:kiit:direct:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb","changedModel":false,"statusText":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.5.4 (325df3e)\n🧠 Model: minimax/MiniMax-M2.7 · 🔑 api-key (minimax:cn)\n🧮 Tokens: 20k in / 209 out\n🗄️ Cache: 50% hit · 20k cached, 0 new\n📚 Context: 20k/204k (10%) · 🧹 Compactions: 0\n📊 Usage: 5h 16% left ⏱2h 13m\n🧵 Session: agent:main:feishu:kiit:direct:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb • updated 16m ago\n⚙️ Execution: direct · Runtime: OpenClaw Pi Default · Think: adaptive · elevated\n🪢 Queue: steer (depth 0)"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778665597259}}
{"type":"message","id":"88ae993c","parentId":"01b4796f","timestamp":"2026-05-13T09:46:58.692Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK, so:- Current context is only 20k/204k (10%) - that's actually good, we have plenty of room- Compactions: 0 (no compaction has happened yet)- Queue depth: 0 (no backlog)\n\nThe session itself is fine. The \"slow\" the user is experiencing is likely just the MiniMax model API being slow in general - not related to context management at all.Let me also check if there's anything relevant in recent logs about why the model might be slow - but I think the key answer here is:1. The lossless-claw IS working - it's managing context at 20k/204k (10%), compactions: 0 - meaning it hasn't needed to compact yet because context is still light2. The slow response is entirely the model API latency (MiniMax), not context management3. \n\nI should also address the user's specific questions: lossless-claw is indeed working as a Context Engine plugin and its effects show up in how well context is preserved and how intelligently it gets compacted, while the improvement in speed they're noticing is probably just the model warming up or network variability rather than any optimization from the plugin itself.","thinkingSignature":"854821e8fdd1bd4b933feb2d980a9edc1857b8cbf26bccad67bfd57ec50d1ab5"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n情况其实比你想的好：\n\n```\nContext: 20k/204k (10%)  ← 轻松，还有 180k 空间\nCompactions: 0          ← 还没触发过压缩\nQueue: 0                 ← 没有积压\n```\n\n**lossless-claw 正在工作**，只是我们今天才装，Context 才 20k，还远远没到需要压缩的阈值（75% = 153k）。\n\n---\n\n## 问题拆解\n\n你说的\"慢\"是两层：\n\n### 1. MiniMax 模型响应慢（主因）\n\n日志里你的 session 经常 `age=585s` 等模型返回——这不是 OpenClaw 的问题，是 MiniMax API 慢。网络抖动、API 负载都会影响。\n\n### 2. 什么企业版？—— 就是 lossless-claw\n\n**它有用**，但不是\"加速器\"，是\"保管箱\"：\n- 传统压缩：把 100 条对话缩成 1 条摘要，丢细节\n- lossless-claw： DAG 结构，保留关键细节，按需展开\n\n对于你们的场景（7~8 个 Agent 协作）：\n- 跨 Agent 的上下文传递更完整\n- 很久以前的重要决策/约定，不会被\"误压缩\"掉\n- 召回工具（lcm_grep/lcm_expand_query）可以直接搜历史\n\n**它不管模型跑多快**。如果 MiniMax 本身响应慢，装什么 Context Engine 都不会变快。\n\n---\n\n## 建议：先跑一天看\n\n今天 MiniMax 响应明显比之前慢，这是 API 端的问题，不是插件能解决的。\n\nlossless-claw 的价值会在**长期、高频、多 Agent 协作**的时候显现——现在才装，还没积累足够多的对话来展示效果。\n\n要不要我写一个简单的测试，让你直观对比一下传统压缩 vs lossless-claw 的区别？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":230,"output":627,"cacheRead":67104,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67961,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778665597275,"responseId":"06537b7d53140e1856448f678378e582"}}
