{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6f70dac6cca8c36760f17efa97d\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-05-13 17:49 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"6a1163a9","parentId":"0d6c5e8e","timestamp":"2026-05-13T09:49:55.199Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"997f4ce1","parentId":"6a1163a9","timestamp":"2026-05-13T09:50:33.850Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is confused. They're asking about \"two\" things I installed for data assistance. Let me think about what they're referring to:\n\n1. `lossless-claw` - the context engine plugin I installed via `openclaw plugins install @martian-engineering/lossless-claw`\n2. Earlier today, there was mention of the \"企业级的 Context-Engine\" from the article they shared about OpenClaw Context-Engine\n\nWait, I only installed ONE plugin - `lossless-claw`. The other one I looked at was `context-engine` from clawhub which turned out to be a different company context engine for C-suite advisors, not the OpenClaw Context Engine. \n \nOh, I see the confusion now - they're referencing the article they sent earlier about OpenClaw Context-Engine, which was presented as a new product for intelligent context management and lossless compression. The user seems to think I installed this alongside `lossless-claw`, but I only installed `lossless-claw`. So `lossless-claw` is actually the real deal - it's the official OpenClaw context engine plugin. That `context-engine` skill I found on clawhub was something completely different, meant for managing company context for advisors, not what we need here. Looking back at what I actually installed versus what was discussed, I only set up `lossless-claw` as the context engine. The other one I looked at was something completely different—a C-suite advisor context loader that wouldn't have helped with conversation management at all. So I should clarify to the user that there was just one installation, and it's already working.","thinkingSignature":"87c4514c499ed846a283171324119b1364daa1846a51dcdc6c0a0ebaeca26a34"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n等等，可能有误解。让我说清楚：\n\n## 今天只装了一个\n\n**`lossless-claw`** — 这就是文章里说的那个\"无损压缩 Context Engine\"的 OpenClaw 官方插件。\n\n另一个 `context-engine`（clawhub 搜出来的）是个**公司上下文加载器**，是给企业高管顾问用的，完全不是一回事，我没有装那个。\n\n---\n\n## 装的那个有没有用？\n\n**已确认在跑**：\n\n```\nPlugins: lossless-claw (enabled, 0.9.4)\nSlots:   contextEngine → \"lossless-claw\" ✅\nDatabase: ~/.openclaw/lcm.db ✅\n```\n\n**实际效果**：\n- 你的会话现在就在用它管理上下文\n- 数据库已经初始化，migration 全部完成\n- 下一次模型调用时 LCM 会参与（ingest → assemble → compact）\n\n**还没感受到差异的原因**：你的上下文还不够长，没触发 compaction。等对话一长，传统压缩会粗暴截断，LCM 会用 DAG 增量压缩保留细节——那时候你才会明显感受到\"它没忘事\"。\n\n---\n\n## 现在的情况\n\n- ✅ lossless-claw 已装且 active\n- ✅ 技能文档已同步到 workspace\n- ⚠️ 慢是 MiniMax 模型问题，不是它\n- 📊 Context: 20k/204k (10%)，还早\n\n要不要等对话变长后手动触发一次 compaction，感受一下 DAG 摘要的效果？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":67795,"output":629,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68424,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778665795225,"responseId":"06537c43f716b70f5b396d6725a62bcf"}}
{"type":"message","id":"a02bbc36","parentId":"997f4ce1","timestamp":"2026-05-13T09:54:06.186Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[message_id: om_x100b6f70ed7418b4c4c521e69c48b56]\nou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb: OK，回到刚才我们说的那个方案吧。\n\n方案原则：以OpenClaw自己的系统互通为原则，让跨境电商团队的成员能够互通协作。\n\n工具选择：飞书作为备用方案，因为飞书的云表格或者多维表格也可以实现相应的功能"}],"timestamp":1778666046163}}
{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6f70ed7418b4c4c521e69c48b56\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-05-13 17:54 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"97b84803","parentId":"a02bbc36","timestamp":"2026-05-13T09:54:06.187Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"dd0be037","parentId":"97b84803","timestamp":"2026-05-13T09:54:40.108Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to go back to discussing the coordination plan. The principles are:\n1. Use OpenClaw's internal messaging system as the primary way for agents to communicate\n2. Use Feishu as a backup (since Feishu can also use cloud sheets/multi-dimensional tables for coordination)\n\nThey also mentioned I said I installed \"two\" things for data assistance. Let me think about what they might be referring to. Looking back at the conversation:\n\n1. lossless-claw - Context Engine (DAG-based conversation summarization)\n2. The other thing they might be referring to... \n\nWait, re-reading the user's message: \"你不是说你装了两个来做这个数据辅助的吗？\" - They're asking about two things I installed for \"data assistance\". \n\n\nI only installed one plugin though - lossless-claw. They might be remembering something else or referring to the skill I set up. Let me move forward with the coordination plan they're proposing, which uses OpenClaw's internal messaging as the primary channel and Feishu as backup, with Feishu's cloud tables and multi-dimensional tables serving as alternative coordination tools.\n\nFor the architecture, I need to establish a shared task pool file in the workspace that the director agent can periodically poll via cron jobs, then use sessions_send to dispatch tasks to sub-agents who execute and write results back to the workspace for director review.\n\nEach agent has its own dedicated workspace directory where it stores files and outputs, so I need to figure out the best structure for the shared task pool and how to set up the cron job on the director agent.\n\nI should create a `tasks/` folder in the director's workspace with a `task-pool.json` file that contains tasks with fields like id, type, from, to, content, status, created_at, and updated_at. Then I'll set up a scheduled check every 30 minutes that uses sessions_send to notify the director, along with a simple task submission format so I can explain this clearly to the user.\n","thinkingSignature":"5708aa2e2f49f3dacd32f1593cbd0f3a1ba421f5332ade15ead168eca1475c23"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n好的，关于\"装了两个\"——我装的是 `lossless-claw`（Context Engine），只有这一个。另外那个是技能文件（SKILL.md），不影响性能，不用管。\n\n---\n\n## 跨境电商团队协作方案\n\n### 核心架构\n\n```\n共享任务池（JSON文件）\n    ↓\nDirector Agent（定时轮询）\n    ↓ sessions_send → 各子Agent\n    ↓\n子Agent执行 → 写回共享文件\n    ↓\nDirector汇总 → 给你汇报\n    ↓\n飞书抄送（备选，人类可看）\n```\n\n### 具体落地\n\n**1. 共享任务池格式**\n```json\n// ~/.openclaw/workspace/director/tasks/task-pool.json\n{\n  \"tasks\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"tk_001\",\n      \"type\": \"选品\",\n      \"from\": \"director\",\n      \"to\": [\"tts\"],\n      \"content\": \"本周主推家居品类，请整理 TOP10 爆款\",\n      \"status\": \"pending\",\n      \"created_at\": \"2026-05-13T18:00:00Z\",\n      \"deadline\": \"2026-05-14T12:00:00Z\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**2. 子 Agent 执行完写回**\n```json\n{\n  \"id\": \"tk_001\",\n  \"status\": \"done\",\n  \"result\": {\n    \"items\": [...],\n    \"summary\": \"TOP10 爆款已整理完成\"\n  },\n  \"completed_at\": \"2026-05-13T19:30:00Z\"\n}\n```\n\n**3. Director 每 30 分钟轮询一次**\n\n---\n\n### 需要确认的事\n\n1. **任务池放哪里？**\n   - A：放在 Director 的 workspace（`~/.openclaw/workspace/director/`）\n   - B：放在共享目录，所有人都能读\n\n2. **谁触发第一棒？**\n   - A：你通过 KIIT 告诉 Director 要做什么 → Director 下发\n   - B：Director 定时自动看飞书多维表格，自己领任务\n\n3. **优先级排序**：你们日常最高频的指令是什么？选品 / 内容 / 投流 / 达人？先把这个链路跑通。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":68094,"output":876,"cacheRead":192,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69162,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778666046198,"responseId":"06537d3e8292b6dacccd424658e988a7"}}
{"type":"message","id":"74d968ae","parentId":"dd0be037","timestamp":"2026-05-13T10:07:58.834Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[message_id: om_x100b6f70990fd0b8c381b960bd4f374]\nou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb: 不是，你不能把问题甩给我呀。通常这种情况是怎么解决？你要给我一个完整的方案"}],"timestamp":1778666878812}}
{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6f70990fd0b8c381b960bd4f374\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-05-13 18:07 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"26dfbfae","parentId":"74d968ae","timestamp":"2026-05-13T10:07:58.835Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"a4d1906e","parentId":"26dfbfae","timestamp":"2026-05-13T10:08:20.028Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"HALEI is frustrated and wants a concrete plan. He's saying I shouldn't just describe options and ask him to decide, I should give him a complete, actionable solution. He wants to know how this is typically solved.\n\nLet me think about what a complete multi-Agent coordination system looks like using OpenClaw's internal messaging (sessions_send) as primary and Feishu as backup.\n\nThe key components needed:\n1. **Task distribution** - Director Agent needs to be able to send tasks to child Agents\n2. **Result collection** - Child Agents complete work and report back\n3. **Shared state** - A common place to track who's doing what\n4. **Human oversight** - The human (HALEI) should be able to see/intervene\n\n\n5. **A practical architecture** - I'll sketch out a working system with a coordinator agent that assigns work, child agents that execute and report back, a shared workspace for state management, and a way for the human to monitor and intervene when needed, all connected through OpenClaw's messaging primitives rather than relying on third-party APIs.","thinkingSignature":"26e464a43ca604bbd6e2b018ef1911e2a396609136fa22ec81d0cf69ac8f9234"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_w6n26meyz7tt_1","name":"update_plan","arguments":{"explanation":"开始搭建多 Agent 协作方案","plan":[{"status":"in_progress","step":"设计 Agent 通信协作方案"},{"status":"pending","step":"搭建共享任务池文件格式"},{"status":"pending","step":"配置 Director 定时协调循环"},{"status":"pending","step":"测试内部互通链路"},{"status":"pending","step":"验证完整流程"}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":68652,"output":345,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68997,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778666878861,"responseId":"0653807fb5e78e08b9eba0c095194ea5"}}
{"type":"message","id":"f2b18572","parentId":"a4d1906e","timestamp":"2026-05-13T10:08:20.160Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_w6n26meyz7tt_1","toolName":"update_plan","content":[],"details":{"status":"updated","explanation":"开始搭建多 Agent 协作方案","plan":[{"step":"设计 Agent 通信协作方案","status":"in_progress"},{"step":"搭建共享任务池文件格式","status":"pending"},{"step":"配置 Director 定时协调循环","status":"pending"},{"step":"测试内部互通链路","status":"pending"},{"step":"验证完整流程","status":"pending"}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778666900159}}
{"type":"message","id":"355e3ff7","parentId":"f2b18572","timestamp":"2026-05-13T10:09:01.606Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me design the complete multi-Agent coordination system. First, let me think about the architecture:\n\n**Principle**: OpenClaw internal communication first, Feishu as backup\n\n**Architecture**:\n1. **Shared Task Pool** - A JSON file in a shared workspace that all agents can access\n2. **Director Agent** - Has a cron job that periodically checks the task pool\n3. **sessions_send** - For real-time direct Agent-to-Agent communication\n4. **Feishu** - For important decisions that humans need to see/approve\n\n**Task Pool Format** (JSON):\n```json\n{\n  \"tasks\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"task-001\",\n      \"type\": \"dispatch\",      // dispatch | report | alert\n      \"from\": \"director\",\n      \"to\": [\"content\", \"koc\"],\n      \"priority\": \"high\",\n      \"content\": \"本周重点做家居品类视频脚本\",\n      \"status\": \"pending\",     // pending | in_progress | done | rejected\n      \"createdAt\": \"2026-05-13T10:00:00+08:00\",\n      \"deadline\": \"2026-05-15T18:00:00+08:00\",\n      \"result\": null\n    }\n  ],\n  \"reports\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"report-001\",\n      \"from\": \"content\",\n      \"type\": \"completion\",\n      \"content\": \"家居视频脚本已完成\",\n      \"taskId\": \"task-001\",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2026-05-13T15:00:00+08:00\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**Director Agent Coordination Loop**:\n1. Every N minutes, Director checks the task pool\n2. For `dispatch` tasks with status `pending`, sends via sessions_send to target agents\n\n\n3. Target agents execute and write results back to the pool\n4. Director reviews the results and escalates to human if needed\n5. Feishu notifications are sent for high-priority items\n\nNow I need to implement this by setting up the shared workspace directory structure, creating the task pool file with the schema, configuring the Director agent to run periodic checks, and writing the coordination prompt that tells Director how to operate.","thinkingSignature":"f2bc2935e444e10da53b082859c0a0b77563103c4128e07f1f85d2cb9933a3ff"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n好，我给完整方案。\n\n## 跨境电商多 Agent 协作方案\n\n### 核心架构\n\n```\n共享任务池（JSON文件）\n  ↕ 读写\nDirector Agent（定时轮询 → sessions_send 下发指令）\n  ↕ sessions_send\n各子Agent（执行 → 写回结果）\n  ↕ 飞书（重要指令抄送 + 人类审批）\nHALEI（你）\n```\n\n---\n\n### 1. 共享任务池文件\n\n在共享 workspace 建一个任务池：\n\n**`~/.openclaw/workspace/tasks/task-pool.json`**\n\n```json\n{\n  \"version\": \"1.0\",\n  \"tasks\": [],\n  \"reports\": [],\n  \"alerts\": []\n}\n```\n\n任务格式：\n\n| 字段 | 含义 |\n|------|------|\n| `id` | 唯一标识（task-001） |\n| `type` | `dispatch`（下发）/ `report`（汇报）/ `alert`（预警） |\n| `from` | 谁发的 |\n| `to` | 发给谁（数组） |\n| `priority` | `high` / `normal` / `low` |\n| `content` | 具体指令内容 |\n| `status` | `pending` → `in_progress` → `done` / `rejected` |\n| `result` | 执行结果 |\n| `createdAt` | 创建时间 |\n| `deadline` | 截止时间 |\n\n---\n\n### 2. 共享 workspace 目录\n\n```\n~/.openclaw/workspace/\n  ├── tasks/\n  │   ├── task-pool.json      ← 任务池\n  │   └── archives/           ← 历史归档\n  ├── shared/\n  │   ├── products/           ← 选品数据\n  │   ├── content/           ← 内容素材\n  │   ├── traffic/           ← 投流数据\n  │   └── koc/               ← 达人数据\n  └── SOUL.md ...\n```\n\n---\n\n### 3. Director Agent 协调循环\n\n给 Director 加一个 **cron job**（每 30 分钟触发一次）：\n\n**Director 做的事**：\n\n```\n① 读 task-pool.json\n② 找 status=pending 的 dispatch 任务\n③ sessions_send → 目标 Agent\n④ 目标 Agent 执行 → 写回 result\n⑤ 汇总结果 → 高优先级发飞书通知你\n⑥ 你可以随时进飞书查看/干预任务状态\n```\n\n---\n\n### 4. 指令下发示例\n\n```\n你（给 Director 发飞书）：\n  \"本周主推家居品类，内容团队出5篇笔记，投流团队准备2000元预算\"\n\nDirector 自动写任务池：\n  → task-001: {to: [\"content\"], content: \"家居品类5篇笔记\", deadline: \"2026-05-20\"}\n  → task-002: {to: [\"traffic\"], content: \"家居品类投流预算2000元\", deadline: \"2026-05-20\"}\n\nsessions_send 发出 → content & traffic 分别执行\n执行完 → 写回 task-pool.json\nDirector 汇总 → 飞书通知你完成情况\n```\n\n---\n\n### 5. 飞书作为备用的场景\n\n| 场景 | 用飞书做什么 |\n|------|-------------|\n| 重要决策需你审批 | 发消息给你，等回复 |\n| 任务完成通知 | 飞书群推送 |\n| 异常预警 | 飞书告警 |\n| 人类干预 | 直接在飞书回复，Director 读取 |\n\n---\n\n### 落地步骤\n\n| 顺序 | 做什么 |\n|------|--------|\n| **①** | 创建共享 workspace 目录和 task-pool.json |\n| **②** | 给 Director Agent 写协调 Prompt（加载路径、读任务池、sessions_send 格式） |\n| **③** | 配置 cron job（Director 每 30 分钟跑一次） |\n| **④** | 测试一条指令的完整链路 |\n\n---\n\n要我开始落地吗？从第①步开始，先把目录和文件建好。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":148,"output":1315,"cacheRead":68640,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":70103,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778666900173,"responseId":"06538094ae91c46350f420ea1d182b0b"}}
{"type":"message","id":"df292f24","parentId":"355e3ff7","timestamp":"2026-05-13T11:30:13.325Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[message_id: om_x100b6f7242fe5cacc4c07c58063c136]\nou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb: 行，你看着弄就行了。总之要好用。\n\n而且现在互通的话，是让跨境电商这个team来互通，后边建其他一阵子的时候就不互通了。这个到时候是不是可以通过选人的方式来很方便地调整呢？"}],"timestamp":1778671813300}}
{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6f7242fe5cacc4c07c58063c136\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-05-13 19:30 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"58c17463","parentId":"df292f24","timestamp":"2026-05-13T11:30:13.326Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"661b5fb3","parentId":"58c17463","timestamp":"2026-05-13T11:30:53.110Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants:\n1. A complete, ready-to-use multi-Agent coordination solution\n2. The ability to easily select which team members (Agents) can communicate with each other\n3. When building new teams in the future, they should be able to choose whether they互通 or not\n\nSo the design needs to be flexible - a team-based permission system where:\n- Team members can communicate internally by default\n- New teams can be created with their own isolated communication pools\n- Cross-team communication can be enabled/disabled selectively\n\nLet me design a complete solution:\n\n**Key Design Principles:**\n1. **Team-based communication** - Agents belong to teams, teams have their own task pools\n2. **Flexible configuration** - Easy to add/remove team members\n3. **Director as coordinator** - Each team has a Director that manages task dispatch\n\n\n4. **Internal first, Feishu as backup** - Use sessions_send for internal comms, Feishu for visibility and human intervention\n\nI'm thinking about the structure: teams each have their own directory under `~/.openclaw/workspace/teams/` with a config file listing members, a shared task pool, and optional team-specific cron jobs. When a new team is created, I'd just add a new directory with its configuration - this keeps everything modular and easy to manage.\n\nFor the cross-border e-commerce team specifically, I need to identify which Agents are involved and define how they communicate, but first I should establish the overall architecture so the solution scales beyond just this one use case.\n\nNow looking at the specific agents in this team: the Director would be the main coordinator, handling task distribution to the TTS for product selection, Content for video and文案 work, Traffic for ad placement, KOC for influencer partnerships, Finance for cost analysis, and Ops for daily operations. The Review agent seems to handle comment analysis and user feedback, though I'm not entirely certain about its exact role yet.\n\nFor the implementation, I'd start by creating a shared task pool file where each task specifies which agent should handle it, then give the Director its own workspace to manage the workflow. The Director would run periodic checks every 30 minutes to pull pending tasks and dispatch them to the appropriate agents, with results flowing back into the pool. Each agent would have a corresponding handler that executes the assigned work and reports completion.\n","thinkingSignature":"0fc5d777239edd8bcf43ce70e80fe16e0c4c9fe11f5d627e38d4e354798302ec"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n明白，我来搭一个完整的、可扩展的方案。\n\n## 完整方案设计\n\n### 架构原则\n\n```\n团队隔离 → 同团队内互通 → 不同团队默认隔离\n     ↓\n灵活配置 → 改配置文件中成员列表即可\n     ↓\n飞书备选 → 重要指令同步抄送，人类可介入\n```\n\n### 核心数据结构\n\n每个团队一个配置目录：\n\n```\n~/.openclaw/workspace/teams/\n├── cross-border/           ← 跨境电商团队\n│   ├── team.conf           ← 成员配置\n│   ├── tasks/\n│   │   └── task-pool.json ← 任务池\n│   └── results/           ← 执行结果\n├── new-team/              ← 新团队可直接复制目录、改名、改配置\n│   └── ...\n```\n\n### 团队配置文件格式\n\n```json\n// team.conf\n{\n  \"team_id\": \"cross-border\",\n  \"name\": \"跨境电商团队\",\n  \"members\": [\"director\", \"tts\", \"content\", \"traffic\", \"koc\", \"finance\", \"ops\", \"review\"],\n  \"coordinator\": \"director\",\n  \"cron_interval_minutes\": 30,\n  \"feishu_notify\": true\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 第一步：创建跨境团队目录和配置\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_z7fq2pnzwgid_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mkdir -p ~/.openclaw/workspace/teams/cross-border/tasks ~/.openclaw/workspace/teams/cross-border/results","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":69358,"output":795,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":70153,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778671813340,"responseId":"065393c6fc8b27d1e743a13c6c02edb6"}}
