{"type":"message","id":"be9c1ae7","parentId":"b2ba09a5","timestamp":"2026-05-13T11:33:12.838Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, the coordinator works. Now I need to:\n1. Set up a cron job to run the director coordinator every 30 minutes\n2. The cron should use sessions_send to actually dispatch tasks to the agents\n\nBut wait - the coordinator script itself doesn't use sessions_send. It just reads the task pool and prints what it would dispatch. The actual message sending needs to happen via OpenClaw agent sessions.\n\nLet me think about the architecture:\n\nOption 1: The cron runs the coordinator script, which then uses `sessions_send` to dispatch\nOption 2: The cron triggers the Director agent, which then reads the task pool and dispatches\n\nOption 2 is better because the Director agent can use the full OpenClaw toolset (sessions_send, memory, etc.) and has context awareness.\n\n\nI'll configure a cron job that runs an agentTurn payload every 30 minutes, instructing the Director agent to check the task pool and send messages to the relevant agents, with the results written back to the results directory. Since I don't have a specific Director agent setup yet, I need to figure out how to send to a sessions_send target.\n\nLooking at the session routing, the Director agent has its own session key under `agent:director:feishu:director:direct:*`, so I can use sessions_send to communicate with it. Now I'll create the cron job that triggers the Director to process the task pool and dispatch messages to tts and content agents accordingly.","thinkingSignature":"543dd0e41f9776dce131a4ae811786df5af5c263bd0b09b6c8bc09c6d429042b"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n调度器跑通了。现在搭定时任务，让 Director Agent 每 30 分钟自动轮询：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_2fgpw5z9lk98_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"{\n  \"id\": \"task_001\",\n  \"type\": \"选品\",\n  \"from\": \"director\",\n  \"to\": [\"tts\"],\n  \"content\": \"整理本周跨境热销 TOP5 品类数据\",\n  \"status\": \"done\",\n  \"result\": {\n    \"items\": [\n      {\"品类\": \"家居用品\", \"GMV\": \"¥12万\", \"增长率\": \"+35%\"},\n      {\"品类\": \"3C配件\", \"GMV\": \"¥9.5万\", \"增长率\": \"+22%\"},\n      {\"品类\": \"户外运动\", \"GMV\": \"¥7.8万\", \"增长率\": \"+41%\"},\n      {\"品类\": \"宠物用品\", \"GMV\": \"¥5.2万\", \"增长率\": \"+18%\"},\n      {\"品类\": \"服装\", \"GMV\": \"¥4.1万\", \"增长率\": \"-5%\"}\n    ],\n    \"summary\": \"本周家居品类表现最佳，3C配件稳定，户外运动增长最快\"\n  },\n  \"created_at\": \"2026-05-13T19:00:00Z\",\n  \"completed_at\": \"2026-05-13T20:30:00Z\",\n  \"deadline\": \"2026-05-14T10:00:00Z\"\n}","path":"~/.openclaw/workspace/teams/cross-border/results/demo_001.json"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":270,"output":642,"cacheRead":72672,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73584,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778671971675,"responseId":"06539464850ae16e86337d8b56b3ccbf"}}
